- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of machine learning for vehicle classification.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper focuses on the use of machine learning algorithms for vehicle classification.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper briefly mentions the importance of ensuring the security of traffic data.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also less likely but possible as the paper discusses the design and deployment of traffic monitoring systems.
